Premise
=======

Shifter is a series about a man who shifts through multiple dimentions without control. He hasn't a clue why he hops from world to world like he does, he only knows that's what he does.

Characters
----------

**John Burke**. Our main character. He shifts from world to world. The only thing that keeps him going is the thought that home might be around the next bend. He helps people on his journy as best he can. He finds it difficult to run into his doubles from time to time.
